{"tid":2530853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特首高官收粉末信 深圳衛視訪問鄧炳強：再次提醒本土恐怖活動隨時有機會發生","createTime":"2021-05-14T17:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T19:30:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b1af055076579b277207ddbfc5990fa1c9b74b2a","tid":2530853,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T17:35:54.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥、保安局局長李家超，以及警務處處長鄧炳強，昨日先後收到一封白色粉末信，案件正由中區重案組跟進。警務處處長鄧炳強今日接受內地傳媒訪問首度回應稱，收信人都是國家安全委員會的主要成員，相信是意圖挑戰特區治安。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強在訪問表示，警方正調查送粉末信的意圖，但從3名收信人來看，相信意圖是挑戰特區治安。他認為，事件反映預防工作有效，因為在信件送到前，已經有機制檢查是否有危險品在內。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強在訪問中指，警察總部曾亦曾收過郵件炸彈，認為今次粉末信事件，是再次提醒本土恐怖活動等只是表面上減退，隨時有機會發生，仍有人尋找機會作「孤狼」式襲擊，故他認為，要居安思危、作好準備。"},{"pid":"6a4791ae0eb963cf693fe506958cdc5fff1088d0","tid":2530853,"uid":48362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T17:38:23.000Z","msg":"都未死得 扮乜撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edce04cd458dab4ebe683744f01d9005a3218a0f","tid":2530853,"uid":52779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />深圳衛視"},{"pid":"f890459ff5b984248d31b0635a4274c8b7bfbc61","tid":2530853,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edce04cd458dab4ebe683744f01d9005a3218a0f","tid":2530853,"uid":52779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />深圳衛視"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class